  "texts": [
    "It is then forwarded to the decoder consisting of two upsampling blocks of the same type.",
    "Each of these blocks expands the spatial dimension of the input feature map.",
    "The first block is responsible for bringing the data into the shape of (8,8,64).",
    "The second block performs similar upsampling but produces an output in the shape of (16,16,16).",
    "The final convolutional layer produces the prediction in the shape of (16,16,1) with sigmoid activation."
  ],
